      "content": "sometimes i sit here in my apartment and the silence is just... so heavy. i work all day on these calls and then i just turn the screen off and it's like i don't even exist anymore. i feel like a ghost in the machine or something. like if i just stopped showing up, would anyone actually even notice?",
