    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "burnout doesn't even capture it. it's more like... knowing that the role i play is totally replaceable. like any of us are. everything is so automated and digital now that nothing really matters. it's almost peaceful to think about just fading out. no big goodbye, no drama, just... exiting the loop. would it even be bad if everything just went quiet like that?",
